  <brief_title>A f-MRI Study Of Affective Changes Associated With Four Weeks Consumption Of A Fermented Dairy Product In Healthy Women</brief_title>
  <official_title>A f-MRI STUDY OF AFFECTIVE CHANGES ASSOCIATED WITH FOUR WEEKS CONSUMPTION OF A FERMENTED DAIRY PRODUCT IN HEALTHY WOMEN</official_title>
  <sponsors>
