  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effect of a commercially available fermented
      dairy product containing probiotics (4 weeks, twice a day) on the brain activity within
      specific neural circuits regulating the subjective experience of emotional valence and
      digestive well-being.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
